cs.IT, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.SI. 

The paper deals with linear inverse problems and regularization techniques, which are common topics in information theory (cs.IT), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of splines and the discussion of multiple solutions also suggest numerical analysis (cs.NA) and signal processing (cs.SI) as possible sub-categories.
